{"tid":794912,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【亞運】呂麗瑤100欄奪銅　港將64年後再揚威田徑個人賽","createTime":"2018-08-26T14:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T00:59:42.000Z","uid":81160,"like":35,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9745cd68fbedee10e75e2ad1bed05b12253a6836","tid":794912,"uid":81160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:51:44.000Z","msg":"「欄后」呂麗瑤在雅加達亞運女子100米跨欄決賽，跑出13.42秒，驚喜奪銅，這個時間更是她的個人最佳時間。香港對上一次奪得田徑個人賽事獎牌，已是1954年的Stephen Xavier，當時他奪得男子200米銅牌。<br />\n<br />\n從早前性侵風波，到今天跨出難關揚威亞運，這面銅牌，對呂麗瑤而言，絕對百感交雜。<br />\n<br />\n香港01記者葉詩敏、鄭子峰　雅加達直擊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/227600/%E4%BA%9E%E9%81%8B%E6%9C%83-2018-%E5%91%82%E9%BA%97%E7%91%A4100%E6%AC%84%E5%A5%AA%E9%8A%85-%E6%B8%AF%E5%B0%8764%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E6%8F%9A%E5%A8%81%E7%94%B0%E5%BE%91%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2F227600%2F%25E4%25BA%259E%25E9%2581%258B%25E6%259C%2583-2018-%25E5%2591%2582%25E9%25BA%2597%25E7%2591%25A4100%25E6%25AC%2584%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E9%258A%2585-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B0%258764%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%258F%259A%25E5%25A8%2581%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%25BE%2591%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%25BD&d=8dzhuo3c3wQVwR160Br7JPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a0a7678c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/227600/%E4%BA%9E%E9%81%8B%E6%9C%83-2018-%E5%91%82%E9%BA%97%E7%91%A4100%E6%AC%84%E5%A5%AA%E9%8A%85-%E6%B8%AF%E5%B0%8764%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E6%8F%9A%E5%A8%81%E7%94%B0%E5%BE%91%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%BD</a><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係me too單嘢我諗佢會上神台"},{"pid":"d5e4cae150a656d4020815ca057c9f232dade441","tid":794912,"uid":42820,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:52:14.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"59017803d131f1b8c76b7d201e8b33e346f09cfc","tid":794912,"uid":4574,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"